sub_title: Division Manager Supply Chain at Sysmex
summary:
As a hands-on person I want to get the job done, preferably with other members of my team. I am a logical, analytical, decisive, commercially trained, business man who relies on the systematic use of concrete facts. Fast thinking and searching for alternative and creative solutions to solve a problem are things I am good at. As a former sales engineer and sales manager I can motivate team members and colleagues or persuade customers, even in difficult and stressful times. 
Being responsible for supply chain gives me the oppertunity to ensure that the right product is delivered at the right customer at the right moment and with the right invoice. And thus, serving our external and internal customer.
